{"tid":2197681,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印媒指控中印邊境解放軍招募藏蒙特種兵 5萬大軍壓境 備妥百架戰機進攻印度。","createTime":"2020-09-10T20:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T23:59:20.000Z","uid":360777,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"84bcd3d6e82e6005c3fe881eeadb012e30f8fe71","tid":2197681,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T20:25:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200910-%E5%8D%B0%E5%AA%92%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%B0%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E8%97%8F%E8%92%99%E7%89%B9%E7%A8%AE%E5%85%B5-5%E8%90%AC%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%93%E5%A2%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200910-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%25B0%25E9%2582%258A%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%258B%259F%25E8%2597%258F%25E8%2592%2599%25E7%2589%25B9%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%2585%25B5-5%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25BB%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%25A2%2583&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=7e964f1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200910-%E5%8D%B0%E5%AA%92%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%B0%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E8%97%8F%E8%92%99%E7%89%B9%E7%A8%AE%E5%85%B5-5%E8%90%AC%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%93%E5%A2%83</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"x-large\">據聯合新聞網今天報道稱，印中軍事衝突持續升溫，印度士兵傳出在邊境對解放軍對空鳴槍示警，打破40多年來邊境不開火默契後，印度媒體連日報導稱，解放軍一邊裝備了比之前流血衝突中所使用的狼牙棒更兇狠的&ldquo;大關刀&rdquo;，準備發動類似於之前造成雙方死傷的突襲之外，解放軍更悄悄動員擅長山地戰的蒙藏後裔、近五萬人規模的大部隊與150架戰機，恫嚇並準備進攻印度。印媒疑似承認印軍士兵對天鳴槍示警。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d34d87c475376e170bfe9050521dc84074439480","tid":2197681,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T20:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\"